### How this becomes a `dashboard_layout` in FastHTML terms

You can think of this file as the “ground truth” HTML. In FastHTML you would essentially:

* Keep the same structure and class names.
* Wrap the outer layout into a function such as `dashboard_layout(content_html)` where `content_html` replaces the inner `main` sections.
* Or keep `main` mostly static and later inject smaller blocks (`stats`, `recent_sessions`, etc.) via HTMX endpoints.

If you want, next step I can:

* Extract this into a `dashboard_layout()` Python function using the FastHTML style you’re already using in `CLAUDE.md`, with a clear `{% content %}`-style slot for your per-page content.

Nice, let’s turn that HTML shell into a reusable `dashboard_layout()` you can drop into your FastHTML app.

Below is a **FastHTML-style Python function** that:

* Wraps the whole DaisyUI drawer dashboard
* Accepts `page_title` and `main_content` so you can reuse it for different pages
* Keeps all the DaisyUI classes intact
* Leaves the stats + “Recent Sessions” + sidebar as placeholders you can later make dynamic

If your exact FastHTML import style is slightly different, you can just tweak the imports / tag names.

```python
from fasthtml.common import *

def dashboard_layout(page_title: str, main_content):
    """
    Generic SKUEL.app dashboard layout shell.

    `main_content` should be a FastHTML node (e.g. Div(...), Section(...), etc.)
    representing the content for the main area of the page.
    """

    full_title = f"SKUEL.app · {page_title}" if page_title else "SKUEL.app"

    return Html(
        lang="en",
        data_theme="corporate"
    )(
        Head(
            Meta(charset="utf-8"),
            Title(full_title),
            Meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"),
            # Link(rel="stylesheet", href="/static/css/output.css"),  # your Tailwind+DaisyUI build
        ),
        Body(cls="min-h-screen bg-base-200")(
            Div(cls="drawer lg:drawer-open min-h-screen")(
                Input(id="main-drawer", type="checkbox", cls="drawer-toggle"),

                # MAIN CONTENT
                Div(cls="drawer-content flex flex-col")(
                    # Top navbar
                    Header(cls="navbar bg-base-100 border-b border-base-300")(
                        # Mobile menu button
                        Div(cls="flex-none lg:hidden")(
                            Label(
                                For="main-drawer",
                                cls="btn btn-ghost btn-square",
                                aria_label="Open sidebar"
                            )(
                                Svg(
                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg",
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24",
                                    fill="none",
                                    stroke="currentColor",
                                    cls="h-5 w-5"
                                )(
                                    Path(
                                        stroke_linecap="round",
                                        stroke_linejoin="round",
                                        stroke_width="1.5",
                                        d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"
                                    )
                                )
                            )
                        ),
                        # Brand / global title
                        Div(cls="flex-1")(
                            A(cls="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight")("SKUEL.app"),
                            Span(cls="ml-2 text-xs opacity-60 hidden sm:inline")(
                                "Game of Life · Askesis"
                            ),
                        ),
                        # Right controls
                        Div(cls="flex-none gap-2 flex items-center")(
                            Button(cls="btn btn-ghost btn-sm", type="button")("Theme"),
                            Div(cls="dropdown dropdown-end")(
                                Label(
                                    tabindex="0",
                                    cls="btn btn-ghost btn-circle avatar"
                                )(
                                    Div(
                                        cls="w-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-content flex items-center justify-center"
                                    )(
                                        Span(cls="text-xs font-bold")("MCF")
                                    )
                                ),
                                Ul(
                                    tabindex="0",
                                    cls="mt-3 z-[1] p-2 shadow menu menu-sm dropdown-content bg-base-100 rounded-box w-40"
                                )(
                                    Li()(A()("Profile")),
                                    Li()(A()("Settings")),
                                    Li()(A()("Sign out")),
                                )
                            )
                        )
                    ),

                    # Scrollable page content
                    Main(cls="flex-1 p-4 lg:p-6")(
                        # Page header
                        Section(cls="mb-6")(
                            H1(cls="text-2xl font-semibold")(page_title or "Dashboard"),
                            P(cls="text-sm opacity-70 mt-1")(
                                "Overview of your learning system, habits, and current focus."
                            ),
                        ),

                        # Stats row (placeholder; later you can parametrize this)
                        Section(cls="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 mb-6")(
                            Div(cls="stat bg-base-100 rounded-box shadow")(
                                Div(cls="stat-title")("Active Learning Paths"),
                                Div(cls="stat-value text-primary")("3"),
                                Div(cls="stat-desc")("Game of Life · EQ · SEL"),
                            ),
                            Div(cls="stat bg-base-100 rounded-box shadow")(
                                Div(cls="stat-title")("Sessions this week"),
                                Div(cls="stat-value")("7"),
                                Div(cls="stat-desc")("Upward spiral in motion"),
                            ),
                            Div(cls="stat bg-base-100 rounded-box shadow")(
                                Div(cls="stat-title")("Habits tracked"),
                                Div(cls="stat-value")("5"),
                                Div(cls="stat-desc")("Coffee · Practice · Reflection…"),
                            ),
                            Div(cls="stat bg-base-100 rounded-box shadow")(
                                Div(cls="stat-title")("Askesis prompts"),
                                Div(cls="stat-value")("12"),
                                Div(cls="stat-desc")("Last 7 days"),
                            ),
                        ),

                        # Main content slot from caller
                        main_content,
                    )
                ),

                # SIDEBAR
                Div(cls="drawer-side")(
                    Label(For="main-drawer", cls="drawer-overlay"),
                    Aside(cls="w-72 bg-base-100 border-r border-base-300 min-h-full flex flex-col")(
                        # Brand block
                        Div(cls="px-4 py-4 border-b border-base-300")(
                            Div(cls="text-lg font-bold leading-tight")("SKUEL.app"),
                            Div(cls="text-xs opacity-70")(
                                "Semantic Knowledge · Upward Spiral"
                            ),
                        ),
                        # Navigation
                        Nav(cls="flex-1 overflow-y-auto")(
                            Ul(cls="menu px-2 py-3 text-sm")(
                                Li(cls="menu-title")(Span()("Main")),
                                Li()(A(cls="active")("Dashboard")),
                                Li()(A()("Learning Paths")),
                                Li()(A()("Askesis Sessions")),
                                Li()(A()("Knowledge Units")),
                                Li(cls="menu-title mt-2")(Span()("System")),
                                Li()(A()("Habits & Metrics")),
                                Li()(A()("Finances")),
                                Li()(A()("Settings")),
                            )
                        ),
                        # Sidebar footer
                        Div(cls="px-4 py-3 border-t border-base-300 text-xs opacity-70")(
                            "SKUEL · v0.1 design shell",
                            Br(),
                            "Made with DaisyUI + Tailwind",
                        )
                    )
                )
            )
        )
    )
